<br>
My testing has shown that the Epic Pet can consistently land his spells/procs on Lvl 61 MOB's.  Only when the MOB's are lvl 62+ do they fail to land.  Back in November of last year, when PoP came out I spent a lot of time in PoV using the Epic Pet in groups killing the Crystalline Golems, since I didn't have my 61 Air &amp; 62 Water pet spells yet. The majority of the Golems are lvl 61 with some being lvl 62.  The Epic pet does tremendous damage to the ones that are 61, but fails to land his spells/procs on the lvl 62 ones.<br>
<br>
Gojirax,<br>
<br>
I use Lucy as the source of my spell damage data.  If you look at the Lucy data:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=848&amp;source=Live" target="top">lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=848&amp;source=Live</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
