<br>
62 Water pet did 38 procs of Wrath of Fire = 38 x 140 damage per proc = 5,320<br>
<br>
What does procing have to do with the pet?  Nothing.  If you want a more accurate parse do it without pet weapons.  Luck of the draw will favor one pet or the other, as in this one, the epic proced 30 more times, nearly double that of the water pet.  thats 2700dmg according to your info.<br>
